description:
“Cock-a-doodle-doo” - which animal makes that sound? Listen alone or with friends to real animal sounds and guess the animal. With each correct guess, you advance to the next, more difficult level, and earn a title! Will you be the first to master all ten levels?

To launch this quiz, say “Start zoo walk”. During the game, you can say "Repeat", "Stop" or "What's the high score". For further assistance, say "Help".
name: Zoo Walk
shortDescription:
A walk in the zoo: Guess animal names by their sounds. Great fun for young and old! Roar!
New and improved version!
